2025-11-21PS, EMCREmergency Management ActProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 286, Newfoundland and LabradorProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 286 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Newfoundland and Labrador with respect to the storm surge that occurred in Newfoundland and Labrador in January 2025.N/A
subject: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 286, Newfoundland and Labrador
precis: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 286 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Newfoundland and Labrador with respect to the storm surge that occurred in Newfoundland and Labrador in January 2025.
